data.description: Newley remodeled to preserve the historic charm! This historic home has all new appliances, stained original hard wood floors, laminate over added spaces, new vanities, completely re-done showers, wood accents, new chandeliers, new kitchen, updated the flow of the home to accommodate entertaining. This is a great chance to own a piece of history while still enjoying all the luxuries of modern life. Located on a corner lot, with a bonus room downstairs and upstairs, this HUGE home is perfect for families, entertaining, or just needing the extra space.
